工厂遍及德国各地，Me-262的零件在夜色掩护下通过卡车、马车
Manufacturer throughout Germany, Sections of the Me-262 were then delivered under cover of darkness by truck, horse and cart,

444
00:37:42,871 --> 00:37:46,710
甚至是自行车运输，然后再森林中组装起来
and even bicycles to be fully assembled in forests.

445
00:37:46,711 --> 00:37:49,050
超过800架是通过这种方式组装起来的
Over eight hundred were to be built in this way.

446
00:37:52,590 --> 00:37:57,240
当越来越多的Me-262被盟军战斗机击落，
But as more and more Me-262 were being destroyed by allied fighters,

447
00:37:57,241 --> 00:37:59,970
德国空军的精英也越来越少
so too with the cream of the German Luftwaffe.

448
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:07,530
