One day a plane came crashing down above me and my plane caught fire.

449
00:38:07,531 --> 00:38:08,460
我只能跳伞
I had to bail out.

450
00:38:09,330 --> 00:38:11,550
这次我只能用降落伞落地了
That's how I had to land with my parachute.

451
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:14,610
对我来说，战争结束了
And that was the end of the war for me.

452
00:38:19,561 --> 00:38:21,480
突然一声巨响
There was suddenly a big bang.

453
00:38:22,100 --> 00:38:26,100
