Even if there had been the production of the Me-262, had ground to a halt,

468
00:39:28,081 --> 00:39:32,760
他们无法生产足够的喷气战斗机来阻止潮水般涌入的盟军
They simply could not build enough jet fighters to stem the tide of the conquering allies.

469
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:43,620
德国最终在1945年5月7日投降
Germany finally surrendered on May, the 7th 1945.

470
00:39:43,620 --> 00:39:46,300
当城市和工厂都被摧毁
As cities and factories were totally smashed,

471
00:39:46,540 --> 00:39:49,560
